#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; helps the software development process by using the industry "
"standard Unified Modelling Language (&UML;) to enable you to create diagrams "
"for designing and documenting your systems."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; pomaga pri procesu razvoja programske opreme z uporabo "
"industrijskega standarda Unified Modeling Language (&UML;), ki vam omogoča "
"ustvarjanje diagramov za načrtovanje in dokumentiranje vaših sistemov."

